Why do you have so much mustard? That's a lot!

250
00:23:02,459 --> 00:23:04,250
You, you...

251
00:23:05,490 --> 00:23:07,490
There's still a lot!

252
00:23:07,490 --> 00:23:10,409
♫ Being silent but miss you ♫

253
00:23:10,410 --> 00:23:12,410
Add some vinegar.

254
00:23:12,410 --> 00:23:13,969
♫ Almost touched dreams ♫

255
00:23:13,970 --> 00:23:15,670
I'll add it for you.

256
