That was my first time drinking beer.

263
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:08,410
How about having some noodles now?

264
00:24:08,410 --> 00:24:10,849
Sure, let's still go to that shop.

265
00:24:10,850 --> 00:24:12,870
- Let's go!
- Go.

266
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:15,409
♫ Love makes ones speechless ♫

267
00:24:15,410 --> 00:24:17,370
