268
00:24:17,370 --> 00:24:20,489
Let's go check it out! It's not far from here, we'll be there in no time.

269
00:24:20,489 --> 00:24:24,930
♫ From the corner of my eyes ♫

270
00:24:24,930 --> 00:24:27,770
