283
00:25:30,610 --> 00:25:32,930
Here are your noodles. Enjoy them.

284
00:25:32,930 --> 00:25:34,269
- Thank you, Ma'am.
- You're welcome.

285
00:25:34,269 --> 00:25:35,810
Thank you.

286
00:25:37,970 --> 00:25:40,450
It even tastes the same.

287
00:25:41,130 --> 00:25:43,410
Are you two studying elsewhere?

288
00:25:44,130 --> 00:25:47,630
No wonder I haven't seen you for long.

289
00:25:47,630 --> 00:25:52,700
You used to come here during snow days and have noodles.

290
00:25:52,700 --> 00:25:54,410
You still remember?

291
00:25:54,410 --> 00:25:56,210
Of course!

292
00:25:57,530 --> 00:25:59,030
Here

293
00:26:01,390 --> 00:26:02,910
That's really great!

294
00:26:02,910 --> 00:26:06,290
Best friends should be like you two.

295
00:26:06,290 --> 00:26:08,430
You are still together when you grow up.

296
00:26:08,430 --> 00:26:10,750
You must cherish this friendship.

297
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:12,410
Enjoy!

298
00:26:15,490 --> 00:26:17,650
Cherish!

299
00:26:22,490 --> 00:26:26,270
Look! Ma'am has always favored me.

300
00:26:26,270 --> 00:26:28,770
She always gives me a lot of mustard.

301
00:26:35,590 --> 00:26:37,870
Add some vinegar.

302
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:41,110
Let's eat!

303
00:26:50,690 --> 00:26:53,770
Your mustard tastes so good.

304
00:26:57,450 --> 00:27:00,370
They've canceled the fireworks show.

305
00:27:00,370 --> 00:27:03,470
The snow has probably dampened them.

306
00:27:34,910 --> 00:27:37,129
Flowers for sale. Flowers for sale.

307
00:27:37,129 --> 00:27:40,270
Sir, want to buy your girlfriend a flower?

308
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,650
You want it?

309
00:27:41,650 --> 00:27:44,050
- Sir.
- How much for one?

310
00:27:44,050 --> 00:27:45,870
Fifteen.

311
00:27:45,870 --> 00:27:47,810
- You like it?
- I like it.

312
00:27:47,810 --> 00:27:49,830
I'll buy them all.

313
00:27:49,830 --> 00:27:52,970
- One hundred for all of these.
- Sure.

314
00:27:56,770 --> 00:28:00,049
- Okay, thank you.
- Happy Valentine's Day! Stay sweet.

315
00:28:00,049 --> 00:28:01,750
Thank you.

316
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:04,329
What do we do? It's too late.

317
00:28:04,329 --> 00:28:08,389
It's okay! I don't like flowers anyway.

318
00:28:11,930 --> 00:28:13,730
Lin Xichi.

319
00:28:14,950 --> 00:28:16,650
What?

320
00:28:21,190 --> 00:28:22,790
What's this?

321
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:24,610
A gift!

322
00:28:31,730 --> 00:28:35,909
I can't open it! Why is there a password? What's the password?

323
00:28:35,909 --> 00:28:37,830
I can't tell you now.

324
00:28:38,490 --> 00:28:40,889
You can keep the password for the rest of your life.

325
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:43,370
You don't want it? Then give it back to me.

326
00:28:43,370 --> 00:28:46,030
It's my gift! You can't take it back.

327
00:28:46,790 --> 00:28:49,230
When will you tell me the password?

328
00:28:52,830 --> 00:28:54,910
That depends on my mood.

329
00:28:54,910 --> 00:28:57,630
In that case, I'll get a locksmith to open it tomorrow.

330
00:28:57,630 --> 00:29:02,570
I'm telling you, if you break the packaging, I'm taking the gift back.

331
00:29:02,570 --> 00:29:03,870
You...

332
00:29:03,870 --> 00:29:05,970
I'll teach you a good lesson.

333
00:29:05,970 --> 00:29:09,010
Be good and wait for the password.

334
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:15,450
- Let's go! Or we'll be late for the bus.
- What bus?

335
00:29:15,450 --> 00:29:18,640
Bus 419. The last ride is at midnight.

336
00:29:42,970 --> 00:29:44,370
Let's go!

337
00:29:55,410 --> 00:29:56,730
Sit here!

338
00:29:56,730 --> 00:29:59,290
No! I can't let others see us sitting together.

339
00:29:59,290 --> 00:30:02,100
I'm Big Brother Chi after all, I need to take care of my name.

340
00:30:02,109 --> 00:30:04,470
You're acting like an idol.

341
00:31:22,970 --> 00:31:25,870
- Feeling sleepy?
- I'm okay.

342
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:31,409
I'll lend you my shoulder, go back to sleep.

343
00:31:31,410 --> 00:31:33,450
No need! I'm not sleepy.

344
00:32:30,490 --> 00:32:32,810
On our marks.

345
00:32:33,690 --> 00:32:35,470
One.

346
00:32:35,470 --> 00:32:36,710
Two.

347
00:32:36,710 --> 00:32:38,310
Three!

348
00:32:39,870 --> 00:32:42,390
I want you to keep doing it.

349
00:32:42,390 --> 00:32:45,490
Keep playing archery and being a captain.

350
00:32:45,490 --> 00:32:47,950
Be a role model for your team members.

351
00:32:47,950 --> 00:32:51,210
Xu Fang, you can do it! You're number one!

352
00:33:05,830 --> 00:33:08,170
Why were you being so careless?

353
00:33:09,300 --> 00:33:11,000
[All Things Bright and Beautiful]

354
00:33:24,990 --> 00:33:27,130
It feels good, doesn't it?

355
00:33:28,090 --> 00:33:31,890
Xu Fang, if I were abandoned by all,

356
00:33:31,890 --> 00:33:34,610
could I really depend on you?

357
00:33:36,250 --> 00:33:39,650
What you said at the restaurant,

358
00:33:39,650 --> 00:33:41,810
do you really mean it?

359
00:33:47,030 --> 00:33:49,770
Did I hurt anyone?

360
00:33:53,970 --> 00:33:55,770
Of course!

361
00:33:55,770 --> 00:34:00,270
If you were to become a homeless, I'd take you in.

362
00:34:08,510 --> 00:34:10,510
Have you had a crush on me?

363
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:49,910
It's the fireworks!

364
00:35:18,990 --> 00:35:20,490
Come here!

365
00:35:22,810 --> 00:35:24,810
Come closer!

366
00:35:25,430 --> 00:35:28,449
- What do you want?
- Come closer!

367
00:35:31,870 --> 00:35:33,870
Look!

368
00:36:30,650 --> 00:36:34,870
The things I planned to do in 3 years initially

369
00:36:34,870 --> 00:36:38,610
