370
00:36:41,550 --> 00:36:44,710
Then, what should I do next?

371
00:36:49,730 --> 00:36:53,290
Stop overthinking!

372
00:36:54,470 --> 00:36:56,750
Why are you talking to yourself?

373
00:36:56,750 --> 00:37:00,649
- Why didn't you knock?
- I did, but you ignored me.

374
00:37:02,070 --> 00:37:03,970
What do you want?

375
00:37:03,970 --> 00:37:07,889
Can I have your revision notes from third year of high school? Give it to me!

376
00:37:08,670 --> 00:37:10,429
This is a miracle indeed.

377
00:37:10,429 --> 00:37:12,750
- Then, just give it to me.
- You've started working hard.

378
00:37:12,750 --> 00:37:15,409
- Do you have it? I need it now.
- You're being possessed?

379
00:37:16,790 --> 00:37:18,390
Do you have it?

380
00:37:19,050 --> 00:37:21,049
Yes, but I need to find it.

381
00:37:21,050 --> 00:37:23,110
I'll give it to you tomorrow.

382
00:37:23,110 --> 00:37:25,110
Sure!

383
00:37:25,110 --> 00:37:27,190
Keep talking to yourself!

384
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:30,689
